# Platypus authors

Platypus is free software (GPL-2.0-only) written by "The Platypus Authors" — the
people and organizations listed below. Copyright is held by the individual
contributors; the source files carry a collective notice
(`Copyright (C) <year> The Platypus Authors`).

Contributions are welcome — open a PR adding yourself to this list (alphabetical by
surname after the founder), as `Name <email-or-handle>`.

## Contributors

Aaron Bauman   — original author and maintainer
